but in a healthy
fat baby way,

60
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:26,875
not in a bad fat baby way.

61
00:02:26,917 --> 00:02:30,250
You know, he's good.
I'm doing a good job.

62
00:02:30,291 --> 00:02:32,291
I'm...

63
