Yeah. Hi.

74
00:02:58,583 --> 00:03:06,000
Yeah.

75
00:03:06,041 --> 00:03:07,792
Okay, Henry.
Look over here.

76
00:03:07,834 --> 00:03:09,792
Look at tigger.
Wave to tigger, honey.

77
00:03:09,834 --> 00:03:11,041
That's a good boy.

78
00:03:11,083 --> 00:03:12,792
Oh, honey, I gotta get
