that's okay.

941
00:36:45,583 --> 00:36:46,750
Or if it's just too much,
that's okay.

942
00:36:46,792 --> 00:36:48,125
But you need to know,

943
00:36:48,166 --> 00:36:49,458
you have to know,

944
00:36:49,500 --> 00:36:53,458
that you will always
be welcome in his home,

945
